<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="bg"><head><meta charset="UTF-8><meta charset="UTF-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /><title>Admin Dashboard - 2L1P Neural Travel</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" /></head><body><div class="topbar"><div class="container topbar-inner"><div><div class="brand-title">Admin Dashboard</div><div class="brand-sub">Search, filter, sort, update statuses, and monitor revenue potential.</div></div><div class="actions"><a class="btn secondary" href="/">Back to Offer Creator</a></div></div></div><div class="container hero"><div class="card"><h2 class="section-title">Dashboard KPIs</h2><div class="kpis" id="adminStats"></div></div><div class="card" style="margin-top:18px;"><h2 class="section-title">Offer Pipeline</h2><div class="filters"><input id="q" placeholder="Search by client, phone, destination, hotel, ID..." /><select id="status"><option value="all">all statuses</option><option value="draft">draft</option><option value="sent">sent</option><option value="viewed">viewed</option><option value="booked">booked</option><option value="cancelled">cancelled</option><option value="expired">expired</option></select><input id="destination" placeholder="destination" /><input id="from" type="date" /><input id="to" type="date" /><select id="sort"><option value="newest">newest</option><option value="oldest">oldest</option><option value="price-high">price high</option><option value="price-low">price low</option></select></div><div id="adminOffers" class="list"></div></div></div><script src="/admin.js"></script></body></html>

